    "English": "Craft Magnetic Resonator from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Magnetized Ferrite</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Ionized Cobalt</span>. Use a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> to process advanced materials.<br><br><span class=\"name name-technology\">Cobalt</span> is found underground. Locate natural cave entrances. <span class=\"name name-red\">WARNING:</span> many caves contain hazardous flora.<br>Gather <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ferrite</span> from planetary rocks.",
